('3a70d36a-ff11-4f32-9c83-7c501467df70', 'dd0020d8-1cd0-40a9-b3fd-1a6a1ddb92a7', 'Cleaning and Lubrication', 'Every 2 weeks', ["Power off the machine and unplug it.","Clean the machine surfaces using a mild detergent and a soft cloth.","Lubricate the specified points as indicated in the user manual.","Remove any debris or swarf from the machine.","Plug in and power on the machine."], 'To prevent build-up of dirt, debris, or rust that can affect machine performance.', 'Regular cleaning and lubrication ensure smooth operation and extend the lifespan of critical components.', 'Ensure the machine is powered off and unplugged before cleaning to prevent electric shock.', 'Prevents premature wear of components and reduces the risk of malfunction.', 'At 700 hours, the machine may start showing signs of dust accumulation and initial wear on moving parts.', ["2025-07-28","2025-08-11","2025-08-25"], '2025-07-09T19:50:51.357228', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
